As the sun began to set and the sky was painted with the
hues of sunset, \N[2] finally mustered the courage to
continue "that" conversation with Luna.

\N<Luna>Phew... It feels like time has flown by since we arrived
here.
\N<\N[2]>Yeah, it really does... Thank you, Luna-chan.

\N<\N[2]>It's because you were with me that I've been able to keep
going until today. Without you, I probably wouldn't have
been able to pay off the debt and by now...

\N<\N[2]>...No, let's not talk about bad things... Instead, Luna-
chan.

\N<\N[2]>I have something I want to tell you... Can I... can I talk
to you about it?

\N<\N[2]>I want to be with you, Luna-chan, from now on and protect
you for the rest of my life. I'll work hard so you won't
have to go through any more hardships...
\N<\N[2]>So, will you... ma, ma... marry me!
\N<\N[2]>(I finally did it, I finally said it!)
\N<Luna>I'm not worthy, but... please take care of me❤

\N<Luna>It's not a dream♪ I'm really happy right now♪
\N<Luna>Come on, don't cry? It's almost time for the ship to depart♪

\N<Luna>No, I don't mind at all~ I love that side of you too, \N[2]-
kun❤
\N<Luna>Ufufu, I'm so happy❤ Then let's go home, to "our" home♪

The story that began with an exorbitant debt demanded on
that day somehow managed to be overcome by Luna and \N[2].

And the proposal that had been put on hold was finally
successful, and the two were happily united.

\N<\N[2]>Gah... What do you want at such an important time... Talk
about bad timing...
\N<Arashi>Ah? Shut up, just back off♪ I came looking for "my Luna."

\N<Arashi>You've been here all this time? Do you have any idea how
long I've been looking for you? Causing me trouble... It's
about time we go "do it"♪
\N<Luna>...Ahh, I'm really sorry, I'll be right there♪

\N<Arashi>Good, I'm seriously horny today, so don't expect any sleep~
I'll be loving you all night long♪

\N<Luna>Ye-yes❤❤❤ Please make my pussy cum lots with your cock,
Arashi-san❤

\N<Arashi>Of course♪... Now, wait for me, hurry up and finish up
here~♪

\N<\N[2]>...Luna-chan, no, it's a lie... right? With that frivolous
guy...
\N<Luna>...No, it's not a lie, I'm serious.

\N<Luna>I have to go to Arashi-san now, I'm sorry \N[2]-kun... this
is "goodbye"...

\N<\N[2]>Wa-wait! I've worked so hard because I wanted to marry
you...

\N<Luna>...When I came to this island, I felt the same way as you,
\N[2]-kun...

\N<Luna>After coming to this island and meeting Arashi-san... I
changed...

\N<Luna>No, that's not right... It's more like I was dyed by him.
Hehe, even though it was a bit forceful❤

\N<Luna>\N[2]-kun, you shouldn't get hung up on me, I hope you find
someone better♪

\N<Luna>I can't keep Arashi-san waiting any longer, so I'm going
now... Bye-bye

\N<\N[2]>A lie... It's a lie, a lie, a lie... a lie... It's a
lieeeeeee!!

Wondering how things ended up this way... \N[2] looked back
on his memories, but it was too late.

Of course, Luna never returned, and when the time for
departure came, \N[2] boarded the ship alone and forlorn.
\N<\N[2]>Do-Dalton-san? What do you want at such an important time...
\N<Luna>Ah, Dalton-san♪ What's up? I told you to wait...

\N<Dalton>Nah, just found another sexy cosplay outfit♪ I couldn't wait
to see Luna-chan in it... hahaha♪

\N<Luna>Ehh, really?～ You're always making me wear so many outfits♪

\N<Dalton>Gufufu♪ With a nice body like Luna-chan's, I want her to

\N<Dalton>That's why you should "break up" here quickly and come to my
place♪ It's going to be a cosplay H marathon until morning♪

\N<\N[2]>...Wait! Please listen to the end of what I have to say...
\N<Luna>I... don't have a reason to be with \N[2]-kun anymore...

\N<Luna>That was "in the past"... But after coming to this island
and meeting Dalton-san, he seemed more reliable than \N[2]-
kun... Maybe it's the maturity of an older man? Being with
him feels so comforting♪

\N<\N[2]>Cosplay H and all that... You're into such hobbies? That's
weird! Such a pervert!!

\N<Luna>...Isn't it "childish" as a person to not be able to accept
other people's hobbies?
\N<Luna>Is it really okay now? I'm going to Dalton-san's place♪

\N<\N[2]>...Wh-why... Why is this happening... There was no sign of
this...

\N<\N[2]>We were supposed to... get married... To have Luna-chan
taken away by such an old man... Damn it...

\N[2], having never imagined the proposal would fail,
continues to wish that the reality before him is just a
dream.

However, as the departure time arrives and the nightmare
does not end, \N[2] boards the ship alone and in solitude.
\N<Bob>I've come to pick you up～♪ Have you said your "goodbyes"?

\N<Bob>Oh, it looks like you're about to do that now～ Sorry, didn't
mean to interrupt.

\N<Luna>I'm sorry, Bob-san... Could you go home first and wait for
me?

\N<Bob>Okay♪ Once you've said goodbye to your boyfriend, come
straight to my home, okay♪

\N<Luna>Yes, of course❤ I'll hurry back♪ When I get there... shall
we do it right away?

\N<Bob>Of course♪ I'll make Luna melt with love all night long
again today～ See you later, I'll be waiting♪
\N<Luna>Sorry, \N[2]-kun, I interrupted you... but I have to go.
\N<\N[2]>Even if I say... I want to marry you...?
\N<Luna>Yes... I can't keep Bob-san waiting any longer.

\N<\N[2]>Wait... why him? Aren't I your boyfriend? Haven't we been
together longer?

\N<\N[2]>Effeminate... where?! I can defeat monsters, and I can earn

\N<Luna>It's different. Bob-san is just too manly... He's amazing,
you know? Very powerful and cool.

\N<Luna>He's reliable as an adventurer during the day, he protects

fufu♪

\N<Luna>That's why... it's goodbye with \N[2]-kun... Take care when
you go back home♪

\N<\N[2]>To break up with Luna-chan... here? To have sex with another
man besides me?

\N<\N[2]>Ah, this is... right, a dream... It must be a dream. I need
to wake up quickly... from this nightmare, quickly...

\N[2] had been waiting for this nightmare to end someday, but
finally, the time for departure arrives and he boards the
ship alone and in solitude.

\N<Syouta>Seriously, Luna! I didn't expect to find you in a place like
this! Since you've become my official apprentice, don't
cause trouble for your boss, me~

\N<Syouta>As punishment, you're in for a spanking tonight~ Be
prepared♪
\N<Luna>Sorry, \N[2]-kun... So, what were you about to say?

\N<\N[2]>Ah... no, it's just... um, I wanted to say... that I want
you to marry me...

\N<Luna>Is, that so... I'm sorry, I can't "marry" you... I have
Syouta-kun now❤

\N<Luna>...Sorry, I have to go now♪ If I make him wait too long, the
punishment tonight will be terrible...
\N<\N[2]>Wa, wait! Why him over me, that kid...
\N<Luna>Don't underestimate the Boss just by his looks...

\N<Luna>You know, as I went to the dungeon with the Boss, I realized
how amazing he is♪

\N<Luna>He may be small and younger... but seeing him work so hard
despite being teased by the other adventurers made me give
my heart and body... and decide to become Syouta-kun's
apprentice

\N<\N[2]>Lu, Luna-chan... It's a lie, right... You're joking, aren't
you?

\N<Luna>Right now, I want to be with the Boss... with Syouta-kun,
more than with you, \N[2]-kun... So it's "goodbye"...

\N<\N[2]>...Luna, chan... My... ugh, ughh... Why did it turn out like
this with Luna-chan... ughh...

And for a while after that, \N[2] held onto the faint hope
that Luna might return...

But that hope was in vain, and as the time of departure
arrived, \N[2] boarded the ship alone and in solitude
